<div class="wikitext">
<a name="perl"></a>
<h1>perl</h1>
<p>
Executes the Perl code, contained in the tag's body text, and returns the result.
</p>
<a name="Summary"></a>
<h2>Summary</h2>

<p>
<ul>
<li><span class="fixedwidth">&#91;perl tables] Perl code &#91;/perl]</span></li>
</ul>

